<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
    <style type="text/css">
    .emailContent{
        font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
    }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body class="emailContent">
    <h1>Your dataset has been created</h1>
    <p>Hi <%= @user.name %>,</p>
    <p>Just a quick note to let you know that your dataset, '<code><%= @dataset.name %></code>' has been created as a private repository in GitHub. It's available to view at the link below:</p>
    <p><%= link_to @dataset.github_url, @dataset.github_url %></p>
    <p>To manage your Octopub datasets, you can access your <%= link_to 'dashboard', main_app.dashboard_url %> at any time.</p>
    <p>Thanks,<br /><br /> The Octopub Team.</p>
  </body>
</html>
